## Input

```css
@if $state == idle {
  color: gray;
} @else if $state == loading {
  color: blue;
} @else if $state == success {
  color: green;
} @else {
  color: red;
}

.layout {
  @if $dense and $touch {
    gap: 0.25rem;
  } @else if $dense {
    gap: 0.5rem;
  } @else {
    gap: 1rem;
  }
}

```


